## 📜 Commands & Permissions

### General Players
* **`/pk`** — Opens the public parkour list to check progress and play.
* **`/pk quit`** — Forces an exit from the current parkour session and restores your freedom.
* *(No extra permissions required; enabled by default).*

### Administrators (`parkour.admin`)
* **`/pka`** — Opens the general Control Panel to oversee and configure everything.
* **`/pka reload`** — Instantly reloads `config.yml` and translation files without restarting the server.
* **`parkour.bypass`** — Allows Admins/Builders to teleport, fly, and break blocks within the area of an active parkour without terminating their session.

